#Plot survival rate for final 5AZA and DMSO concentrations used in downstream experiments. Time_point column referes to treatement window
survival_rate_plot <- survival_rates %>% filter(Time_point %in% c("0-12","DMSO","Control") , uM %in% c("5","DMSO","Control")) %>%
  mutate(Time_point= recode(Time_point,`0-12` = "5-AzadC")) %>% mutate(Time_point=factor(Time_point,levels = c("Control","DMSO","5-AzadC"))) %>%
  pivot_longer(-c(Time_point,uM)) %>% group_by(Time_point) %>% mutate(rate= (value/max(value))*100) %>%

Summarise results
